<lb n="1"/>śrīmānabhūjjagati dhānyapurādhinādhaḥ prakhyātakīrttiramarēśvarapādabhaktaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> mānādivarggavanitāvadanāraviṁda<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrībhīma
