<lb n="3" break="no"/>patiṁ śrīriva padmanābhaṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] śākābdā<unclear>nāṁ</unclear> pra<unclear>mā</unclear>ṇē karagirikhaśasikhyāta vaiśākhamāsē śuklaikādasyacāpē bahutaraphaladē savyatīpāta
